Somehow 5 whole years have passed since you left and life was flipped upside down. The pain and heartache you go through isn’t something that you could ever put into words and is something that will never go away; time doesn’t heal all wounds but it does help you to develop your own set of tools to be able to first cope then to build and progress. As I’ve gotten older with more understanding I’d only wish to have one last conversation and to show you some pictures / videos of what I’ve been upto in this crazy world but hopefully you’ve been watching the entire time ♥️🕊️
